title: Yoshimasa Electronic DSSF3 v5.2.0 Incl. Emulator-R2R [deepstatus
description:
Yoshimasa Electronic DSSF3 v5.2.0






Turn the standard laptop PC into the Highest-grade virtual measurement instrument. DSSF3 is equipped with powerful and easy to use spectrum analyzer, oscilloscope, recorder, and other professional analyzing capabilities. Try this great tool for all sound engineering work!

DSSF3 is a combination of three components: Real-time Analyzer ( RA ), Sound Analyzer (SA), and Environmental noise Analyzer (EA).



Upgraded DSSF3 to version 5.2.0.8

Improved system cooperation of RA and MMLIB.
Added Multi-Screenshot function to DSSF3, Menu bar on RA > Tools > Transfer to MMLIB.
It works during and after measurement.
note:It is alwaysnecessary to specify MMLIB executable file in Setting utility before using.
It stored and recorded not only measuring window but also all windows such as setting window as image files differently from the conventional transfer function.
The image file uses shooting date/time as the filename.


System

Windows 8 / 7 / Vista/ Xp / NT4 / 2000 / Me



Installation:

             

              1. UnRaR

              2. Uninstall previous versions.

              3. Install.
 PCAE3.exe -> English
 PCAJ3.exe -> Japanese

              4. Overwrite with our emulator.
 RegistE.dll -> English
 RegistJ.dll -> Japanese
